globals.abstract: THOR is a mobile Tesla bot, it is a radio controlled vehicle that has the capability of harnessing thousands of volts of electricity as well as RF jamming. The machine will also contain a researched Mobile Tesla Technology also known as M.T.T
globals.catch: Imagine this, Thor, in a robot.
